Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 920
Set Height 620
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 16
Set TypingSpeed 30ms

Sleep 300ms

Type "cd /tmp/demo-saas"
Enter
Sleep 300ms

Type "onerules --force"
Enter
Sleep 4s

Type "onerules doctor"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "head -40 CLAUDE.md"
Enter
Sleep 6s

Sleep 2s
